<div class="container">

<h1>[% book.title %]</h1>

<ul>
<li>[% l( 'Title' ) %]: [% book.title %]</li>
<li>[% l( 'ISBN' ) %]: [% book.isbn %]</li>
<li>[% l( 'Date' ) %]: [% book.date %]</li>
<li>[% l( 'Pages' ) %]: [% book.pages %]</li>
</ul>

<h2>[% l( 'Files and items' ) %]</h2>

<ul>
[% FOREACH f IN book.files %]
    <li>
        [% l( 'File' ) %] [% f.id %] [% l( 'from' ) %] [% f.provider.name %]
        <ul>
        [% FOREACH i IN f.items %]
            <li>
                [% l( 'Item' ) %] [% i.id %] [% l( 'belonging to' ) %]Â [% i.library.name %]
                [% IF i.deleted == 1 %]- [% l( 'Deleted' ) %][% END %]
                [% IF i.loan %]- <span style="color: red; font-weight: bold;">[% l( 'On loan' ) %]</span>[% END %]
            </li>
        [% END %]
        </ul>
    </li>
[% END %]
</ul>

<p>Are you sure you want to delete this book, including its files and items?</p>

</div>
